style:
These court shoes are a versatile addition to your collection. Designed with a high stiletto heel for an elegant look. Insolia® technology redistributes weight away from the balls of your feet, increasing ankle stability and comfort. Antibacterial padding keeps everything feeling fresh.
 M&S Collection: easy-to-wear wardrobe staples that combine classic and contemporary styles.

Item details: Heel Height for Ladies Size 4 Shoe: 80mm

Features: Insolia® technology redistributes your weight away from the balls of your feet, reducing pressure and increasing ankle stability, allowing you to wear your heels comfortably, for longer
antibacterial foam padding minimises odour for all-day comfort
Free from animal-derived ingredients or materials

Composition: Upper: Other materials, Lining and Sock: Other materials & textile, Outsole: Other materials
